        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1489567081" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12662733370037903694">It&apos;s a klunky play, that relies heavily on realism, and really has no reason why it should be presented in a theatre. That being said the central problems of the characters are handled in an unmelodramatic way. Compelling arguments are had and the myth of the noble lower class is laid to waste. A bleak but arresting conversation. </span>
  <span id="freeText12662733370037903694" style="display:none">It's a klunky play, that relies heavily on realism, and really has no reason why it should be presented in a theatre. That being said the central problems of the characters are handled in an unmelodramatic way. Compelling arguments are had and the myth of the noble lower class is laid to waste. A bleak but arresting conversation. </span>
